comments: Melton (PHI) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) perimeter shot attempt.
Niang (PHI) establishes himself in Green's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together during the pick.
Embiid (PHI) firms up on his right leg and does not deliver contact to Poole (GSW) while setting the pick.
Green (GSW) extends and immediately retracts his hand from Niang's (PHI) front and the contact at the beginning of the drive is marginal.
Niang (PHI) loses control of the ball during his gather and the arm contact with Green (GSW) is considered incidental.
Niang (PHI) bobbles the ball during his gather and does not take any additional steps after legally recovering the ball.
Thompson (GSW) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Green (GSW) legally contests Embiid's (PHI) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Looney's (GSW) hand brushes Melton's (PHI) back during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
Melton (PHI) attempts to step around Curry (GSW) and marginal contact occurs.
Melton (PHI) legally contests Poole's (GSW) perimeter shot attempt.
Niang (PHI) establishes himself in Thompson's (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the screen.
Green (GSW) and Harris (PHI) come together at the same spot on the floor and the contact is marginal.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in Thompson's (GSW) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the pick.
Green (GSW) jumps alongside Maxey's (PHI) path and absorbs the marginal contact during the driving shot attempt.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in Melton's (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the pick.
Niang (PHI) legally contests Curry's (GSW) driving shot attempt.
Green (GSW) brings his arm towards the ball and marginal contact occurs with Harris (PHI).
Looney (GSW) retreats in Embiid's (PHI) path and absorbs the marginal contact at the start of the drive.

Replay review of the foul called on Looney (GSW) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Looney  does not have his arm in a legal vertical position when arm contact occurs with Embiid (PHI) that affects his shot attempt in the post.
Melton (PHI) aligns along Curry's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Maxey (PHI) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of the fourth quarter and overtime.
Looney (GSW) legally contests Maxey's (PHI) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) and Embiid (PHI) make simultaneous contact with the loose ball and deflect it away from each other.
Melton (PHI) extends his arm toward the ball and marginal contact occurs with Curry's (GSW) arm.
Niang (PHI) commits a take foul on Thompson (GSW).
Green (GSW) legally contests Springer's (PHI) driving shot attempt.
